          <div class="bb-tagstack">
            <div class="bb-tagitem"><span class="bb-tagnum">01</span><span class="bb-tagtext">"Rapdad, back at it like a crack addict — can't quit if I wanted to."</span><span class="bb-tagctx">Primary Signature</span></div>
