          <div class="bb-stitle">THE LOOK OF<br>UPBEAT PAIN</div>
          <div class="bb-twocol">
            <div>
              <p><strong style="color:#e8edf2;">Aesthetic Direction:</strong> Dark, sleek, city-built. The visual language of a person who came up in the shadows. Not loud. Not flashy. <em style="color:#c8a96e;">Sharp.</em> Like a samurai who also skates. Bandana with Cartier frames and makes it feel inevitable.</p>
              <p><strong style="color:#e8edf2;">Visual References:</strong> Nighttime cityscapes. Long curly hair in a bun against a dark skyline. Scarred face lit dramatically — the scars are not hidden, they're the story.</p>
              <p><strong style="color:#e8edf2;">Photography Direction:</strong> Low-key lighting. Blue and grey tones with warm amber accents. Character over beauty. No heavy retouching. This face has been somewhere.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
